29 bn::matrix<double> createUniformDurationMatrix(vector<Task *>* tasks, double dist) {
30 
31  bn::matrix<double> dm(tasks->size(), tasks->size());
32 
33  for (unsigned i = 0; i < tasks->size(); ++i) {
34  for (unsigned j = 0; j < tasks->size(); ++j) {
35  if(i == j) {
36  dm(i, j) = 0;
37  }
38  else {
39  dm(i, j) = dist;
40  }
41  }
42  }
43 
44  return dm;
45

196 int Scheduler::findTaskNow()
